description._content: Original Caption: Lobster Fisherman's Gear at Conch Key During the Off-Season at This Time the Fishermen Repair Their Traps and Repaint Their Floats. Each Man Has an Identifying Color and Number. Thousands of Traps Are Stored All over the Little Island.
